The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Mirwaiz

 New Delhi, Feb. 1: The Centre has welcomed Hurriyat leader Mirwaiz Umer Farooqs statement in Pakistan asking militants to shun violence.

 The Mirwaiz will be in the capital on Sunday to prepare the ground for a meeting between the Prime Minister and the moderate faction of the Kashmiri separatist amalgam.

 The Prime Minister today gave the go-ahead to his interlocutors to arrange the meeting.




